# PRD-033 FR-3 — Discord egress allowlist (tinyproxy Filter, FilterDefaultDeny On).
# Each line is an extended regex matched against the request HOST. ONLY these hosts
# are reachable through the proxy; everything else (incl. all RFC1918/LAN/FedPulse)
# is denied and logged. Keep MINIMAL.
#
# Covers: REST API + webhooks (discord.com), the realtime gateway WSS
# (gateway*.discord.gg / *.discord.gg), and CDN/attachments
# (cdn.discordapp.com, media.discordapp.net). Voice (discord.media) deliberately
# omitted — the gateway is a text bot, not a voice client.

# REST API + webhooks
^discord\.com$
# Realtime gateway (shard hostnames like gateway-us-east1-b.discord.gg)
(^|\.)discord\.gg$
# CDN + media attachments (anchored exactly; NO `*.discordapp.com` wildcard — the bot
# only needs these two, and a wildcard would widen egress + shadow these anchored lines)
^cdn\.discordapp\.com$
^media\.discordapp\.net$
